      "type": "MARKDOWN",
      "mode": "jshell",
      "source": "# Welcome to Venus Notebooks\n\nVenus is an interactive **Java notebook environment** powered by JShell — like Jupyter, but for Java.\n\n- Run Java code cell-by-cell, with live output\n- Variables persist across cells in the same session\n- Use the **AI Assistant** (Ctrl+\\\\) for code help and generation\n- Install Maven packages from the **Packages** tab\n\nPress **Run All** in the toolbar to execute every example below, or run cells individually with Shift+Enter.",
