      "type": "CODE",
      "mode": "jshell",
      "source": "//@ anchor: declare-variables-they-stay-in-scope-f\n//@ description: Declare variables — they stay in scope for the rest of the notebook\n// Declare variables — they stay in scope for the rest of the notebook\nvar projectName = \"Venus\";\nvar features    = \"JShell, AI Assistant,Package Manager,Markdown Cells\";\nvar releaseDate = java.time.LocalDate.of(2026, 3, 8);\nSystem.out.println(\"Project: \" + projectName);\nSystem.out.println(\"Released: \" + releaseDate);\nSystem.out.println(\"Features: \" + features);",
