      "source": "## 10. Installing Packages\n\nGo to the **Packages** tab to install Maven Central libraries.\n\n1. Enter a coordinate like `com.google.code.gson:gson:2.10.1`\n2. Click **Install** — the JAR is downloaded automatically\n3. Use it in any code cell:\n\n```java\nimport com.google.gson.Gson;\nvar gson = new Gson();\nSystem.out.println(gson.toJson(Map.of(\"hello\", \"world\")));\n```\n\n**Popular packages** are listed as quick-install buttons in the Packages tab.",
